    "141314 Fig. 13 Prediction and uncertainty heatmaps on an example slide in the external test set.",
    "Heatmaps of HPV predictions and uncertainty were generated from the final tile-based model for a randomly selected slide from the test set.",
    "Two areas are shown with magnified display.",
    "Area 1 is a location with intermediate predictions and high uncertainty, showing mostly stroma and out-of-focus cells in the top-right corner.",
    "Area 2 is a location with strong HPV-negative predictions and low uncertainty, showing heavy keratinization and pleomorphic nuclei Fig. 1515 Fig."
